{"tid":1309371,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【社區福利】良心企業 吉野家","createTime":"2019-07-12T07:21:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T08:43:06.000Z","uid":14259,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c87d1d520f64b999c2036bd1da2e3e2fa55c5077","tid":1309371,"uid":14259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:21:41.000Z","msg":"今日最高氣溫有成33度，真係好熱熱呀<br />\n最心痛就係見到老人家熱死辣辣，仲喺條街同公園妹下妹下，就算睇完娜娜跳脫衣舞，都唔夠消暑清熱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想要免費娛樂區啫？我有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n身為孝子賢孫，愛好社區的年輕人，當然非常擔心佢哋會熱親啦，老人家病咗可大可小㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但吉野家就有無限冷氣供應，落地大玻璃非常開揚，坐成日都唔怕侷促<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2ad946V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2ad946V.png&h=66f77cb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舒適寬敞的坐位，直頭唔驚坐到生痔瘡，仲有大大張枱可以捉棋、睇報紙，一個唔覺意想瞓個晏覺，又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n排排坐仲可以同大媽玩個speed dating 迎接第二個春天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v3cyNma.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv3cyNma.png&h=6b80e69f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n等孫仔孫女放學，都唔使驚悶呀，吉野家設有大量差電位，只要拎條電線，就可以安心上網睇大戲喇，喇叭開到幾大聲都唔驚冇電啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fo2fgfc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFo2fgfc.png&h=ba8ebb75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n方便到總有一間喺你咗近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/As7CuAj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAs7CuAj.png&h=4412ff85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎到場耍樂，各位愛錫老人家的年輕人，仲唔帶公公婆婆叔叔嬸嬸去參觀吓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v3kgK9h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv3kgK9h.png&h=47d4bfb9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S336nVY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS336nVY.png&h=ee9d5218&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V40AgfZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV40AgfZ.png&h=eb614356&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JzuJp9k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJzuJp9k.png&h=4a52737d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UOSGbPn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUOSGbPn.png&h=c7c1fe8a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gN8x2V3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgN8x2V3.png&h=b690c91f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ueFc2V4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FueFc2V4.png&h=2f92ddf4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OatmWf5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOatmWf5.png&h=e9fba5a8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VW2by2M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVW2by2M.png&h=cbba1b9c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4BHKT2N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4BHKT2N.png&h=08a11295&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c16bb9f672599ed859732a1325fd8f1e8d4bdb0d","tid":1309371,"uid":135211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:43:06.000Z","msg":"廢老又多個選擇"}]}